  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Our logistics company is looking for a <strong>Business Development Executive</strong> to drive revenue growth, expand market reach, and establish strategic partnerships. The role includes:</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Lead Generation &amp; Sales:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Identify and approach potential clients (manufacturers, retailers, e-commerce businesses, etc.).</li>\n  <li>Develop and execute sales strategies to close deals.</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain a strong sales pipeline.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Client Relationship Management:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Foster relationships with existing clients to encourage repeat business. Address client concerns and provide tailored logistics solutions</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Market Research &amp; Strategy:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Analyze industry trends, competitors, and customer needs.<br>\nDevelop strategies to position the company ahead of competitors.<br>\nIdentify new revenue streams (e.g., last-mile delivery, warehousing, cold chain logistics).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Partnership &amp; Vendor Management:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Establish partnerships with transportation providers, warehouses, and suppliers.<br>\nNegotiate contracts and pricing for cost-effective solutions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Marketing &amp; Branding</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work with the marketing team to promote services via digital marketing, trade shows, and networking events.<br>\nDevelop proposals, presentations, and marketing materials.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Operational Collaboration</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate with internal teams (operations, fleet management, customer service) to ensure seamless service delivery.</li>\n  <li>Provide client feedback to improve service offerings.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s degree in Business, Marketing, Logistics, or a related field.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in business development, sales, or a related role within the logistics, transportation, or supply chain industry.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication, negotiation, and relationship-building skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and meet sales targets.</li>\n</ul>",
